osoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌库存合并扣减：一种基于分布式缓存的强一致性热点库存扣减方案</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&amp;mid=2247556956&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=71861533b18d95d2f7f4ece75ca776b5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_ezTVydFszZnc0ZN-JEtlQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_ezTVydFszZnc0ZN-JEtlQ</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍一种在热点深库存扣减场景下的库存合并扣减方案，将分布式缓存（Redis）用于扣减计数以提升性能，同时以库存扣减明细作为最终的正确性依据，确保不超卖且不少卖，并通过分桶缓存、合并提交、以及自动锁库存等机制实现强一致性与高吞吐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44907407407407407\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" width=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"501968511\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2076dccc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FMzFz9Kf2u1NkGGPsaicQhlPulLoDc2p5jxfgOb2cyYflYJoXLTFQnhicWib21TQibB7FXX8SweuQQeib1bvCzNF9kr9Uu5dT2GtH1ibaicCoArHCnc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌文本大模型评测实践</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247507396&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ac034c55fa33c8cb0e05655e6cf2f621&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/U4YyYbRsGt65TsW9qESKXQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/U4YyYbRsGt65TsW9qESKXQ</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文提出以“维度-指标-评测集”为核心的文本大模型评测框架，结合货运行业场景，形成货拉拉特色的半自动化评测实践，并实现了在邀约、客服等场景的落地应用。通过对近三年国内外评测成果的梳理，提出通用、领域、场景三大能力维度，以及数据集构建、评测流程、评测方式（人工、机器、人机协同）等要素，强调数据质量、安全性与可解释性的综合考量，最终构建了面向实际业务的评测闭环与落地方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6805555555555556\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" width=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"501968512\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f191ff27&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FMzFz9Kf2u1Py0NWBxErd3VA8ylmS3ibIHAKYIHzHkx3icWTBMQdibETGrIYfKM9fWMoeicqHWhpCqsNGHIM7LUCMeQmm6sz9e8ar6ADOFoRia0rU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌拆解 Open WebUI：前端如何做一个生产级 AI 对话界面</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MzIyMDM5Ng==&amp;mid=2649865149&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=aa93c29f6cce93a6d4121e6ac3c0d69a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/CadWp459rXi-lH2su6zTBQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/CadWp459rXi-lH2su6zTBQ</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文从前端开发的视角拆解 Open WebUI 的实现，总结其将生产级 AI 对话界面做成的关键设计思路：以 Svelte/SvelteKit 架构实现高效前端、通过树状消息结构实现对话分支与回溯、采用流式渲染及性能优化策略、使用富文本输入框提升交互体验、以及通过插件体系实现功能扩展与配置驱动的扩展性。同时给出在实现中应关注的取舍点与可迁移的学习要点，强调架构思路胜于直接照搬实现细节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7462962962962963\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" width=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"501968513\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0904b0b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FMzFz9Kf2u1O3YbS02YDfD749wB7pibuXAUwI4e77UNeFmOnuT48znPQfPY68YP7JkdHZCPsibiakzEfj1o9pm4BJDPhcLq5ONqfj2lenBjhZlI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌AI Coding思考：从工具提效到范式变革，我们还缺什么？</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650542970&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=231a9b78e5c7e1054aa26e86556e8ed8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/4AXThfVLmhSXeRWK1gh4dA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/4AXThfVLmhSXeRWK1gh4dA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文围绕企业级软件研发场景下的 AI Coding 提效进行深度思考，指出当前AI Coding虽工具繁多、执行能力提升迅速，但在真实生产中尚未实现“质变式提效”，其核心瓶颈在于如何准确、高效、规模化地将复杂任务目标传达给AI，并由此引出需要体系化、结构化、可自动化的专家知识库来降低信息熵，从而实现从“工具提效”向“知识驱动的智能研发范式变革”过渡，最终促使程序员角色从编码者向“产品工程师/业务架构师”转变，研发流程实现需求—设计—编码—验收的全链路 AI 协同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5092592592592593\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" width=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"501968514\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06995bdc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FMzFz9Kf2u1Nib2ib5mcD5UkIESsgqJHibAjl2yNkoCRL9YwHuvdwDAZicezxmFPEOEViaFDx2iaCAXryafmgZAVTvicQiayzo0XCibHptrE24SMIibzgc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌货拉拉待办中心架构设计：打造高效可靠的任务中枢</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247507274&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4bf2ba710e1bbb7e3a6c4bf5b6b7a2b0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/5NSCAyhIeIf6XDrpamrcDg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/5NSCAyhIeIf6XDrpamrcDg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍货拉拉待办中心的架构设计，围绕“标准化、性能优化、解耦扩展”三大目标，提出通过领域驱动设计提炼共性、以本地化查询与缓存实现毫秒级响应、以及领域事件实现异步解耦的待办中心方案，解决接口稳定性、低延迟和业务扩展性三大挑战，并通过三种生命周期管理模式、三层流量控制和场景化扩展设计，支撑亿级以上的待办数据和高并发查询，同时提供稳定的监控、容错和数据一致性保障，最终实现从被动响应到主动赋能的业务转型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4537037037037037\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" width=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"501968515\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b51b1a5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FMzFz9Kf2u1MiaribCM2947wwm5fW5Y8euca14WMGP7kEoZCsP8JZGYIQCf5XITsZu4dWXKRAFWpH2S5zdXuDEye9hDV0e9JE1LzqJr4lv4HqI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌取代Figma的新神器？Paper：设计、代码与AI Agent的完美融合</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyOTc4NjE2NA==&amp;mid=2247495067&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7b985652430936308e62c46f9d9d7cdf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/sT9FiW96SAXHQwkH9FALCw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/sT9FiW96SAXHQwkH9FALCw</a></span></sp